{"tid":808163,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母印度仔個是但午餐POST出未?日日上CHILD登就係等呢一刻","createTime":"2018-09-06T06:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T10:06:50.000Z","uid":16697,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e6fa92930a1c85ccb2284115d78ef8c847713e97","tid":808163,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:37:42.000Z","msg":"更新版 9字頭電話號碼已被棄用<br />\n<br />\n一剔過<br />\nA、B、C、D餐係固定午餐<br />\n而E、F、G、H餐係每星期都轉一次<br />\n連埋蒜包餐湯凍飲 原價$45 / 48 / 50蚊<br />\n1230前埋單 / 1415後入坐減5蚊<br />\n盛惠$40 / 43 / 45蚊<br />\n推介菜式係皇牌燒雞 + 避風塘脆薯皇<br />\n星期六會送埋甜品 暫時係焦糖燉蛋<br />\n有緣仲會見到連登飲食台台柱<br />\n受薪中立飲食評論打手&mdash;慘過番印度<br />\n<br />\n百里香 觀塘駿業街67號熟食市場1樓44號<br />\n路線：港鐵觀塘站A2出口 步行約6分鐘<br />\n營業時間：一至五11:00-16:30；六11:00-16:00<br />\n外賣熱線：67082851"},{"pid":"93ec52563bed6bc8f556e217849d86088610680b","tid":808163,"uid":25028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"老細未過數"},{"pid":"61e61d5b951bf145187f58431c8b0c28a07b8acb","tid":808163,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"今日不得閒出去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c242d18f6e057990bde5eb953530ff81ff7d94ec","tid":808163,"uid":110758,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"61e61d5b951bf145187f58431c8b0c28a07b8acb","tid":808163,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"今日不得閒出去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"你仲有咩存在意義?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45b15678227daa56e0eae9ffd2b33d27a0859fd","tid":808163,"uid":16697,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"61e61d5b951bf145187f58431c8b0c28a07b8acb","tid":808163,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"今日不得閒出去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/it